long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Super Oliver World is an arcade game available as a Chrome extension where you help little Oliver escape the dangers of a parallel world full of traps and dangerous enemies. Break blocks to find power-ups, coins, and other surprises along the way!


. A or left arrow key = move left
. D or right arrow key = move right
. W or Z or up arrow key = jump
. X or J = shoot

If you want play more game, press "Unblocked Games, Web Version" to find more games on our website:  https://monkeymart.org/, https://drivemad.org/, https://eggycar.org/, https://geometrydash.ee/
